Feature: DemoQA Elements Section Navigation
As a user
I want to navigate through the Elements section
So that I can access all element components


Background:
Given user is on DemoQA Elements page


Scenario: Open Text Box section
When user opens Text Box
Then Text Box page should be displayed



Scenario: Open Check Box section
When user opens Check Box
Then Check Box page should be displayed


Scenario: Open Radio Button section
When user opens Radio Button
Then Radio Button page should be displayed


Scenario: Open Web Tables section
When user opens Web Tables
Then Web Tables page should be displayed


Scenario: Open Buttons section
When user opens Buttons
Then Buttons page should be displayed


Scenario: Open Links section
When user opens Links
Then Links page should be displayed


Scenario: Open Broken Links and Images section
When user opens Broken Links and Images
Then Broken Links and Images page should be displayed


Scenario: Open Upload and Download section
When user opens Upload and Download
Then Upload and Download page should be displayed


Scenario: Open Dynamic Properties section
When user opens Dynamic Properties
Then Dynamic Properties page should be displayed